do this:
./configure
make

your executables will be in the bin directory and the source is in the src 
directory.


timers: A timer that operates off of a thread. the timer uses setitimer system
timer to as the timer/clock

timers1: same as timers but uses posix create_timer() instad of setitimer()

timers2: a full but immature setitimer() timer API example program with 
classes

timers4: same as timer2 except that the API is much more mature, potential bugs
are eliminated, algorythms have been tightened and signal handling is a bit more 
solid. Comments are added as well.

